stimulus:
Transcript Annotation Task

In this task, you will:

  1. Read a transcript of someone solving a math puzzle
  2. Use the provided buttons to insert code templates
  3. Fill in the templates to annotate what the person did

For each trial:

  • Click buttons to insert code templates
  • Edit the text as needed
  • Click Submit when you're done to move to the next trial

Press any key to begin
